<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    <p>Welcome! ðŸ‘‹</p>
    <p>This web app consumes the <a href="http://localhost:1337">local strapi API</a> to display any siteVisitors defined in the strapi admin.</p>
    <div>
      {{#if siteVisitors}}
        <h2>Site Visitors retrieved from local strapi API</h2>
        {{#each siteVisitors }}
            <h3>{{ this.name }}</h3>
            <p>{{this.email}}</p>
        {{/each}}
      {{else}}
        <h3>Local strapi API returned no siteVisitors at this time.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Make sure your strapi API is running locally.</li>
          <li>Make sure the siteVisitors content type, in the strapi api app, has permission to return data</li>
          <li>Try adding siteVisitors at: <a href="http://localhost:1337/admin">http://localhost:1337/admin</a></li>
        </ul>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    <article>
      <h3>Notes</h3>
      Please find the corresponding <a href="https://strapi.training">strapi.training</a> video at: (TBD)
    </article>
  </body>
</html>


